# Bake the cc-toolchain's compile+link command lines into cc_wrapper and forward
# them on every invocation, so C invocations that bypass GHC's -optc/-optl path
# (Cabal checkForeignDeps, ./configure, c2hs, GHC's link-time C stub) still get
# the hermetic sysroot/header/CRT/runtime flags. Generated bazel-out paths carry
# the wrapper's exec config and are re-resolved per invoking action at runtime.
